# This is a simple Ecommerce Shopping  user guide/ 
 
# To instal the Ecommerce : 
 
# 1-Create a database in mysql type: utf8-general ci. 
# 2-Execute the file .sql | you will find it named ecommerce.sql 
# 3-Go to config / database.sql and: 
a- set your hostname 
b- set your username 
c- set the password 
d- set the database name. 
 
# 3-enjoy